[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]认可同性[[民事结合|民事结合]]，将會于2013年7月1日认可[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]<ref name=ABCNews>{{cite news|last=Chase|first=Randall|title=Delaware to Become 11th State With Gay Marriage|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/delaware-senate-vote-gay-marriage-bill-19126528#.UYl0KkqH_To|accessdate=7 May 2013|newspaper=[[ABC_News|ABC News]]|date=7 May 2013|archive-date=2013-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509161049/http://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/delaware-senate-vote-gay-marriage-bill-19126528#.UYl0KkqH_To|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年5月1日，州长签字通过同性结合法案，该法案“赋予同性伴侣与注册婚姻同样的权利、利益、保护和责任”。同性结合法案于2012年1月1日生效<ref name=WDDE>{{cite news|last=Byrne|first=Tom|title=Delaware becomes 11th state to approve same-sex marriage|url=http://www.wdde.org/43765-delaware-approves-same-sex-marriage|accessdate=May 7, 2013|newspaper=WDDE|date=May 7, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131229085636/http://www.wdde.org/43765-delaware-approves-same-sex-marriage|archivedate=2013年12月29日}}</ref> 。2013年，特拉华州75法案在众议院和参议院均获通过，州长[[杰克·马克尔|杰克·马克尔]]在法案上签字。同性婚姻法案将于2013年7月1日生效，届时特拉华州将成为美国第十一个同性婚姻合法的州。

==民事结合==
2011年3月，特拉华州参议员大卫·索科拉和梅拉妮·乔治提出同性婚姻法案<ref>{{cite web |work=News Journal |url=http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20110323/NEWS02/103230356/-1/health03/Civil-unions-bill-filed-Dover |first=Beth |last=Miller |title=Delaware government: Civil unions bill filed in Dover |date=March 23, 2011 |accessdate=April 13, 2011}}</ref>。该提案于2011年3月31在州管理服务委员会通过<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20110331/NEWS02/103310353/Civil-unions-bill-clears-committee|title = Delaware civil unions bill clears committee|author = Beth Miller|publisher = [[The_News_Journal|The News Journal]]|date = 31 March 2011|access-date = 2013-05-09|archive-date = 2011-04-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110403034207/http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20110331/NEWS02/103310353/Civil-unions-bill-clears-committee|dead-url = no}}</ref>，4月7日在州参议院以13－6获得通过<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.washingtonblade.com/2011/04/07/del-senate-passes-civil-unions-bill/ |title=Delaware Senate passes civil unions bill |first=Lou |last=Chibbaro Jr. |work=Washington Blade |date=April 7, 2011 |access-date=2013-05-09 |archive-date=2019-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011035757/https://www.washingtonblade.com/2011/04/07/del-senate-passes-civil-unions-bill/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，4月14日在州众议院以26－15获得通过<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20110414/NEWS/110414059/Delaware-adopts-civil-unions-bill |title=Delaware adopts civil unions bill |first=Beth |last=Miller |work=The News Journal |date=April 14, 2011 |access-date=2013-05-09 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923223117/http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20110414/NEWS/110414059/Delaware-adopts-civil-unions-bill |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月11日，州长杰克·马克尔在法案上签字并发表感言<ref>{{cite news|last=Mucha|first=Peter|title=Same-sex unions legalized in Delaware|url=http://articles.philly.com/2011-05-12/news/29536491_1_civil-unions-lesbian-couples-full-marriage-rights|accessdate=January 23, 2013|newspaper=Philadelphia Inquirer|date=May 12, 2013|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071257/http://articles.philly.com/2011-05-12/news/29536491_1_civil-unions-lesbian-couples-full-marriage-rights|dead-url=no}}</ref> ：

{{quote|<!--Tonight, with the signing of this law, we say to any Delawarean, regardless of sexual orientation, if you have committed yourself to somebody, and you've made that pledge to spend your life together in partnership, your love is equally valid and deserving, your family is now equal under the law.-->今晚，在签署这项法案后。我们对所有的特拉华人说，不论你的性倾向如何，如果你对某人作出承诺，并发誓两人将共度余生，那么你们的爱，你们的家庭在法律下就是平等的。}}

该法案于2012年1月1日生效。在2012年间，特拉华共发出了565张结合证明<ref name=license>{{cite news|first=Ashley|last=Dawson|url=http://delaware.newszap.com/centraldelaware/118809-70/number-of-civil-unions-exceeded-expectations|publisher=newszap|title=Number of civil unions 'exceeded expectations'|date=December 30, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106045548/http://delaware.newszap.com/centraldelaware/118809-70/number-of-civil-unions-exceeded-expectations|archivedate=2013年11月6日}}</ref>。其中250张来自[[苏塞克斯县_(特拉华州)|苏塞克斯县]]，235张来自[[纽卡斯尔县|纽卡斯尔县]]，80张来自[[肯特县|肯特县]]。2014年7月1日，特拉华州将不再签发民事结合证书，已存在的同性结合将转换为婚姻<ref>{{cite web|work=Pam's House Blend|url=http://pamshouseblend.firedoglake.com/2013/05/07/delaware-becomes-eleventh-state-to-legalize-marriage-equality/?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|first=Laurel|last=Ramseyer|title=Delaware Becomes Eleventh State to Legalize Marriage Equality [Updated]|date=May 7, 2013|accessdate=May 7, 2013|archive-date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224234749/http://pamshouseblend.firedoglake.com/2013/05/07/delaware-becomes-eleventh-state-to-legalize-marriage-equality/?utm_source=twitterfeed&utm_medium=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==同性婚姻立法==
2012年3月，州长杰克·马克尔认为同性婚姻合法化在特拉华州是大势所趋，相关法案很可能在未来几年通过<ref>{{cite news|title=Delaware governor says gay marriage is "inevitable" in his state|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/02/us-usa-gaymarriage-delaware-idUSTRE82116K20120302|accessdate=16 December 2012|newspaper=Reuters|date=March 2, 2012|archive-date=2012-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120423113319/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/02/us-usa-gaymarriage-delaware-idUSTRE82116K20120302|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2012年9月，代表彼得·施瓦茨科夫表示希望州立法会能投票支持同性婚姻。他个人支持同性婚姻，但也表示出对立法前景的不确定<ref>{{cite news |last=Starkey |first=Jonathan |title=Schwartzkopf: gay marriage a "no-brainer" |url=http://blogs.delawareonline.com/firststatepolitics/2012/09/26/schwartzkopf-gay-marriage-a-no-brainer/ |accessdate=December 16, 2012 |newspaper=DelawareOnline |date=September 26, 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118085444/http://blogs.delawareonline.com/firststatepolitics/2012/09/26/schwartzkopf-gay-marriage-a-no-brainer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年2月1日，[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]][[天主教威尔明顿教区|威尔明顿教区]]主教威廉·马卢尼对教区教友发信呼吁“婚姻是一男一女之间的契约，必须得到珍惜和捍卫”<ref>{{cite news|title=Head of Catholic diocese in Delaware takes aim at gay marriage in pastoral letter|url=http://articles.washingtonpost.com/2013-02-01/national/36677069_1_gay-marriage-civil-unions-pastoral-letter|accessdate=February 4, 2013|newspaper=Washington Post|date=February 1, 2013}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。2013年4月，关于将同性婚姻合法化并取消民事结合的法案递交到立法院。威廉主教向立法院写信抗议，表示“婚姻不仅关于爱和承诺，并且是一男一女分别作为丈夫和妻子给对方的独一无二的爱。婚姻不仅是一个标签，而且具有宗教神圣感，不能存在于同性之间。“<ref>{{cite news|title=Marriage is not for government to 'define or redefine,' says bishop|url=http://www.catholicsun.org/2013/04/17/marriage-is-not-for-government-to-define-or-redefine-says-bishop/|accessdate=May 7, 2013|newspaper=The Catholic Sun|date=April 17, 2013|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919090519/https://www.catholicsun.org/2013/04/17/marriage-is-not-for-government-to-define-or-redefine-says-bishop/|dead-url=no}}</ref>该法案分别在众议院和参议院获得通过<ref>{{cite news |last=Ford |first=Zack |title=BREAKING: Delaware To Become 11th State With Marriage Equality |url=http://thinkprogress.org/lgbt/2013/05/07/1975311/breaking-delaware-to-become-11th-state-with-marriage-equality/ |accessdate=May 7, 2013 |newspaper=Think Progress |date=May 7, 2013 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407083938/https://thinkprogress.org/lgbt/2013/05/07/1975311/breaking-delaware-to-become-11th-state-with-marriage-equality/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Dawson|first=James|title=Same-sex marriage bill clears state House|url=http://www.wdde.org/42982-same-sex-marriage-passed-house|accessdate=April 23, 2013|newspaper=WDDE|date=April 23, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512174813/http://www.wdde.org/42982-same-sex-marriage-passed-house|archivedate=2013年5月12日}}</ref>。在法案获得两院通过后一小时内州长即签字，法案于2013年7月1日生效<ref name=ABCNews />。州参议员卡伦·彼德森于同年5月7日出柜，成为特拉华州第一位出柜的[[LGBT|LGBT]]立法委员<ref>[http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/07/karen-peterson-gay_n_3232462.html "Karen Peterson, Delaware State Senator, Comes Out During Gay Marriage Debate"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/05/07/karen-peterson-gay_n_3232462.html |date=20160320003941 }}. ''[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]]'', May 7, 2013.</ref>。

==公众意见==
2011年2月，公共政策民意调查进行的一样测验显示，48％的特拉华投票人支持同性婚姻，47％的投票人反对，8％不确定<ref>{{cite web |work=Delaware Liberal |url=http://www.delawareliberal.net/2011/02/09/large-plurality-of-delaware-supports-marriage-equality/ |title=Plurality of Delaware Supports Marriage Equality |date=February 9, 2011 |accessdate=April 13, 2011 |archive-date=2018-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921112050/http://www.delawareliberal.net/2011/02/09/large-plurality-of-delaware-supports-marriage-equality/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年3月6日，大湖研究伙伴进行的测验显示62％的投票人支持同性结合，31％的投票人反对，7％不确定<ref>{{cite web |work=Delaware same-sex partnership |url=http://equalitydelaware.org/uploads/BroadSupport_PressRel_EQDE_110316.pdf |title=Delaware same-sex partnership support |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021173315/http://equalitydelaware.org/uploads/BroadSupport_PressRel_EQDE_110316.pdf |archivedate=2012-10-21 }}</ref> 。2013年2月，全球战略集团的民调显示，54％的投票人支持同性婚姻，37％的投票人反对，8％的人不确定或拒绝回答<ref name=EqualityDelaware>{{cite web|url=https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/equalitydelaware/pages/54/attachments/original/1362425933/Equality_Delaware_Press_Release_-_New_Poll_54__Support.pdf?1362425933|title=New Poll: 54% of Delaware Voters Support Marriage Equality|publisher=EqualityDelaware|date=March 4, 2013|access-date=2013-05-09|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317050415/https://d3n8a8pro7vhmx.cloudfront.net/equalitydelaware/pages/54/attachments/original/1362425933/Equality_Delaware_Press_Release_-_New_Poll_54__Support.pdf?1362425933|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=GSGPoll>{{cite web|url=http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20130304/NEWS/303040048/Poll-least-half-Delaware-s-voters-would-support-same-sex-marriage?nclick_check=1|title=Poll: At least half of Delaware's voters would support same-sex marriage|publisher=delawareonline|date=March 4, 2013|access-date=2013-05-09|archive-date=2016-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128102632/http://www.delawareonline.com/article/20130304/NEWS/303040048/Poll-least-half-Delaware-s-voters-would-support-same-sex-marriage?nclick_check=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

